    <h2>Form input element with type as checkbox</h2>
    <h3>Checkbox is used to select <span>many options</span> in <span>many option</span></h3>
    
    <form>
        <h4>Interests:</h4>
        <input type="checkbox" id="coding" name="interest" value="coding">
        <label for="coding">Coding</label><br>
        
        <input type="checkbox" id="music" name="interest" value="music">
        <label for="music">Music</label>
    </form>

    <p>We can use <b>checkbox</b> to select more than one option.</p>
